ides new answers to an old question: why are Judean hagiographies so unusual?  This approach firmly links the works to their institutions, and envisions them as the textual element of larger hierotopic constructions.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 10. Jan 2022) 0aChristian hagiographyxHistoryyTo 1500. 0aChristian saintszByzantine EmpirevBiographyxHistory and criticism. 0aChristian saintszByzantine EmpirexBiographyxHistory and criticism. 0aChristian saintszJudaea, Wilderness ofvBiographyxHistory and criticism. 0aChristian saintszJudaea, Wilderness ofxBiographyxHistory and criticism. 0aChristian saintszJudean DesertvBiographyxHistory and criticism. 0aChristian saintszPalestinevBiographyxHistory and criticism. 0aChristian saintszPalestinexBiographyxHistory and criticism. 0aMonastic and religious lifexHistoryyEarly church, ca. 30-600. 0aMonastic and religious lifezJudaea, Wilderness of. 0aMonastic and religious lifezJudean Desert. 0aMonastic and religious lifezPalestine. 4aAntiquities & Archaeology. 4aReligion. 7aRELIGION / Antiquities & Archaeology.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2020 Englishz978311070477808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2020z9783110704570oZDB-23-DGF08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertGorgias Press Complete eBook-Package 2020z978311068958740uhttps://doi.org/10.31826/978146323982440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781463239824423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781463239824/original  